Honda Auto Receivables 2016-2 Owner Trust –
HONDA AUTO RECEIVABLES 2016-2 OWNER TRUST, as Issuer, AMERICAN HONDA FINANCE
CORPORATION, as Sponsor and Administrator, AMERICAN HONDA RECEIVABLES LLC, as
Depositor, and Citibank, N.A. As Indenture Trustee ADMINISTRATION AGREEMENT
Dated May 31, 2016
(May 31st, 2016)
This Administration Agreement, dated May 31, 2016 (this "Agreement"), is among Honda Auto Receivables 2016-2 Owner Trust, as issuer (the "Issuer"), American Honda Finance Corporation ("AHFC"), as sponsor (in such capacity, the "Sponsor") and administrator (in such capacity, the "Administrator"), American Honda Receivables LLC ("AHR"), as depositor (in such capacity, the "Depositor"), and Citibank, N.A., as indenture trustee (the "Indenture Trustee").



